name: Peacemaker Keychain by Crranky
description:
The year was 1791. A pretty cool thing happened. Yeah, that. So spread the word and keep the peace the old fashioned way.

The Peacemaker Keychain is a part of the Apocalypse Series.

Includes thick-heavy 13 gauge, 1.5" diameter, stainless steel Peacemaker medallion, 2 color hand screen printed chipboard package and 6 inch steel cable keychain.

Crafted with attitude in Kansas, USA.

name: Skkully Bottle Opener by Crranky
description:
Introducing the first ever Crranky Brand original and exclusive product, the Skkully Bottle Opener with Keychain.

Only one thing speaks to your identity more than the beer you drink and that would be the bottle opener you use. Time to get this awesome, rugged tough and well, freakin cool Skkully Bottle Opener by Crranky..

Ok sure, you may be the type to throw back a Grape Nehi now and then. But that’s ok. You can still show everyone that you’re really a Hell’s Angel inside. That’s right, no matter who you are you can adorn the Crranky Skull Bottle Opener with the included steel keychain with your backpack, motorcycle keys, rearview mirror or around your lady’s neck.

The Skkully Bottle Opener Art Packaging is cool enough to keep on your desks or on your wall. And trust us, you’ll want to keep the packaging. Crranky. Cool. Stuff. just got original.

Includes thick-heavy 13 gauge Stainless Steel Skully Bottle Opener, chipboard letterpress printed package and 6 inch steel cable keychain.

Crafted with attitude in Kansas, USA.

name: Immpy Defense Bottle Opener by Crranky
description:
Following up on the successful launch of the Skkully Bottle Opener we now bring you Immpy The Self Defense Bottle Opener by Crranky.

We realize you are probably no whimp – you can defend yourself in almost any circumstance that doesn’t involve a WMD. So if you need a different reason to sport this little devil of keychain bottle opener, why not use it for a beer can vent?

You’re a lover not a fighter, you say. Ok, we hear ya. So then just be yourself and pop open your fav bottle of suds and get tons of attention like, “hey what’s different about you?” Don’t answer, just let them take a close up view of Immpy. They will be red with lusty envy.

Then again, there’s only one thing you bring to a fist fight and that’s a self defense keychain, like say… ours. And think about your lady. She needs one too on those long and lonely nights when you are out with the boys.

Now let’s talk abou the Immpy Bottle Opener Packaging. What can we say, we love designing the Immpy graphic almost as much as we love using the Immpy Bottle Opener itself. You won’t want to throw it away. It’s plenty cool enough to keep on your desk or on your wall or in that manly man cave of yours.

Includes 13 gauge Stainless Steel Immpy Self Defense Bottle Opener, chipboard letterpress printed package and 6 inch steel cable keychain. 

Crafted with attitude in Kansas, USA.

name: Xxipper Zipper Pull by Crranky

Crafted with attitude in Kansas, USA.
